    "id": "section8-federal-rules-2024",
    "name": "Section 8 Housing Choice Voucher Federal Eligibility Rules (2024)",
    "description": "Federal baseline Section 8 Housing Choice Voucher eligibility rules for 2024. Section 8 provides rental assistance to help low-income families, elderly, and disabled individuals afford decent, safe, and sanitary housing in the private market.",
    "version": {
      "major": 1,
